node.text:
[⌚️watch to win an apple watch]
set up and get ready with me to do some work! a productive session with good lighting, new notion template (video coming next week), @owaves.co digital app, pomodoro timer, mechanical keyboard, muji gel pen and bubble tea🧋

°˖✧ what you can win (6 winners) ✧･ﾟ
first place: Apple Watch, $500 Visa gift card, Owaves mugs
second place: $300 Visa gift card, Owaves mug
third place: $200 Visa gift card, Owaves mug
fourth place: $100 Visa gift card, Owaves mug
fifth place: $50 Visa gift card, Owaves mug
sixth place: Owaves mug and dry fit Owaves t-shirt 

°˖✧ how to enter the contest ✧･ﾟ
this contest is hosted by @owaves.co, winner will be randomly selected. contest will run from august 19 - october 15, 2021 

1. download the owaves app, IOS only at this time
2. explore how to use the app (you can add me @revisign)
3. create a daily entry, screenshot your day in review circle, crop to square
4. screenshot the blank template in this reel, fill out all information on instagram, then share to your story for 24 hours! MUST tag @owaves.co for entry to be valid! 

anddddd that’s it! wishing everyone a productive and happy school year ahead🤍
